description:
This code synthesises training data and trains a neural network for quantitative susceptibility mapping (QSM) with the DEEPOLE approach. 
 &nbsp; 
 For details about the method, please refer to the following publication:&nbsp; 
 Jochmann et al. (2025) Quantitative susceptibility mapping in magnetically inhomogeneous tissues. Magnetic Resonance in Medicine,&nbsp;https://doi.org/10.1002/mrm.30537. 
 &nbsp; 
 When using the code or the data, please cite the corresponding paper. Thank you.

